org.terrier.matching.dsms
Class BooleanScoreModifier

java.lang.Object
  org.terrier.matching.dsms.BooleanScoreModifier
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, DocumentScoreModifier
public class BooleanScoreModifier
extends Object
implements DocumentScoreModifier, Serializable

If not all the query terms appear in a document, then this modifier zeros the document's score.
